This demonstration showcases how AI automatically organizes financial documents received via email into 						the correct monthly folder in OneDrive.

					Step 1: Send A Financial Document
					
					A financial document is sent from a finance email account with an Excel attachment

					Step 2: Detect Incoming Email

					Microsoft Outlook automatically detects the incoming email and triggers the n8n automation workflow		
					
					Step 3: Download the Attachment

					The workflow automatically downloads the attached financial document for further processing.

					Step 4 : AI Analyzes the Document

					The AI agent analyzes the filename to identify the billing period and automatically creates the appropriate 						monthly folder in OneDrive.

					Step 5: Organize the Document

					The financial document is automatically uploaded into the correct OneDrive folder, completing the entire process 					without manual intervention
